Description: These personalized tote bags make perfect promotional products which are excellent for stores, schools, clubs or for any of your promotional events. This LISTING INCLUDES a 1 color & 1 location imprint, which can be your team name, company name, logo, slogan, or whatever else you would like. All of the info and details for this specific product are located under the item specs section. Please make sure to review it, so you can see the size of the product, material, features, max imprint area for screen printing, etc. If you would like this product in a different quantity, please check out our other listings or contact us for info. Our normal production time is 7 - 8 business days after final artwork is approve, before your order is completed and shipped out. Once shipped, it will take an additional 1 - 5 business days for your order to arrive, depending on where you're located in the USA. Please note, the FREE shipping offer is ONLY good for the lower 48 US states & doesn't include Hawaii, Alaska, Puerto Rico, US Virgin Islands, Guam, etc. If you're located in one of those US States or territories and would like to make a purchase, please contact us prior to purchase to determine shipping costs. Pick Your Choice From The Following Selections: 1. Product Color(s) - You can mix up to 5 different product colors at 50 pieces per color. Available Product Colors - Red, Royal, Forest (Dark Green), Lime (Light Green), Orange, Pink, Purple, Navy (Dark Blue), Yellow, Black, and Ivory. Our stock changes daily, so please feel free to contact us prior to purchase, if you would like us to check stock for you. 2. Imprint (Text and/or Logo/Design) All submitted artwork must meet our requirements for imprinting and be approved, before we can begin production on your order. Please feel free to contact us anytime, so we can help answer any questions that you may have in regards to your artwork, logo, or design. We will provide you with a basic artwork proof to approve, prior to starting final production on the order. 3. Font Style (If Applicable) - You get to pick your choice of a stock font style to imprint all your text in on the product. Please see image #2 that we have included on this listing, so you can pick your choice of a font style from our list of stock font styles. If there is a specific font style that you would like to use, which we do not have on our stock list, please contact us to let us know which one. 4. Ink Color - You get to pick your choice of a stock ink color to imprint your text and/or logo/design in on the product. Please see image #3 that we have included on this listing, so you can pick your choice of an ink color from our list of stock ink colors for this specific product. If there is a specific ink color that you would like to use, you can choose your own from the PMS color chart for an additional fee. Please contact us for details and info. If you need more than a 1 color and 1 location imprint, please contact us for info and to determine pricing.
